<div id="review_3704135725" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3704135725" />
    <a title="Janalyn Prude" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/72361283-janalyn-prude"><img alt="Janalyn Prude" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1575413875p2/72361283.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3704135725?book_show_action=true">Dec 19, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Janalyn Prude" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Janalyn Prude" href="/user/show/72361283-janalyn-prude">Janalyn Prude</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3704135725" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1860018517378437917">Hunter is a 14-year-old boy who has autism and paranormal abilities. He could see peoples auras and taste and hear their different emotions, in some cases he can even change their oras, but he has yet to get the full grasp of how to do it. I absolutely love the book. Hunter suffered a great loss to him that causes his own aura to be gray he worries and so when a classmate needs his help he doesn’t know if he can help and that is pretty much the just of the book but they also have so much more to</span>
  <span id="freeText1860018517378437917" style="display:none">Hunter is a 14-year-old boy who has autism and paranormal abilities. He could see peoples auras and taste and hear their different emotions, in some cases he can even change their oras, but he has yet to get the full grasp of how to do it. I absolutely love the book. Hunter suffered a great loss to him that causes his own aura to be gray he worries and so when a classmate needs his help he doesn’t know if he can help and that is pretty much the just of the book but they also have so much more to it Ian it was so interesting I read it all in one sitting. I believe this is a book for older children but I must say I thoroughly enjoyed this book. It is one I highly recommend to anyone who likes paranormal stories. I love the authors writing style and the easy flow to the narrative I just totally love this book! It was so cute and one I highly recommend!</span>
