        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3722173735" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10532782730271617381">The Taste of Despair by Darin Brown is the third book in this series and I enjoyed it just as much as the first two, if not more as I found that I could relate to this one as I’m sure other readers will too as most of us have battled with inner demons at some point! <br/>A well written, well researched novel combined with with great characters and an even better plot with many twists and emotions to experience. I recommend that you read the first two books in the series if you haven’t already.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


